com.qualcomm.hardware.lynx.commands

Class LynxDatagram

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qualcomm.hardware.lynx.commands.LynxDatagram

  • public class LynxDatagram
extends java.lang.Object
    A LynxDatagram represents the quantum of transmission of Lynx data between host and controller module.
